SubjectGambler First Nation Indian Reserve 63B, in Manitoba
PrecisOrder setting apart 3.062 hectares (7.57 acres), including mines and minerals, for the use and benefit of the Gambler First Nation, as a new reserve to be known as GAMBLER FIRST NATION INDIAN RESERVE 63B, in Manitoba.
